        <h2>Help and Support</h2>
        
        <section>
            <h3>Getting Started</h3>
            <p>Welcome to the Budget Claims System. This guide will help you navigate through the system and make the most of its features.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Login:</strong> Use your email and password to log in to the system. If you don't have an account, contact support at <a href="mailto:support@budgetclaims.com">support@budgetclaims.com</a>.</li>
                <li><strong>Dashboard:</strong> After logging in, you will be redirected to your dashboard. Here, you can see an overview of your activities and navigate to other sections of the system.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <h3>Submitting a Claim</h3>
            <p>To submit a new claim, follow these steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Navigate to the "Submit Claim" page from the dashboard or the navigation menu.</li>
                <li>Fill out the claim form with the required details:
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>MVA Number:</strong> Enter the 8-digit Motor Vehicle Accident (MVA) number of the car involved.</li>
                        <li><strong>Description:</strong> Provide a detailed description of the claim, including any relevant information about the incident.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Click the "Submit Claim" button to send your claim for processing. You will receive a confirmation email once your claim is submitted successfully.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <h3>Viewing Claims</h3>
            <p>To view the status and details of your submitted claims, follow these steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Navigate to the "View Claims" page from the dashboard or the navigation menu.</li>
                <li>Here, you will see a list of all your claims with the following information:
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>MVA Number:</strong> The MVA number of the car involved in the claim.</li>
                        <li><strong>Description:</strong> A brief description of the claim.</li>
                        <li><strong>Status:</strong> The current status of the claim (e.g., Open, Closed).</li>
                        <li><strong>Date:</strong> The date the claim was submitted.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Click on a claim to view more details and any updates related to that claim.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <h3>Updating Account Settings</h3>
            <p>To update your account settings, follow these steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Navigate to the "Settings" page from the dashboard or the navigation menu.</li>
                <li>Here, you can perform the following actions:
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Reset Password:</strong>
                            <ol>
                                <li>Enter your current password.</li>
                                <li>Enter your new password.</li>
                                <li>Click the "Reset Password" button to update your password.</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Enable/Disable Two-Factor Authentication (2FA):</strong>
                            <ol>
                                <li>Click the "Enable 2FA" button to set up 2FA. Follow the instructions to scan the QR code with your authenticator app and verify the token.</li>
                                <li>To disable 2FA, click the "Disable 2FA" button.</li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <h3>Receiving Notifications</h3>
            <p>You will receive notifications for important events such as new claims, status updates, and reminders for pending tasks.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Email Notifications:</strong> Ensure your email address is up-to-date to receive notifications.</li>
                <li><strong>In-App Notifications:</strong> Notifications will also be displayed within the system for real-time updates.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <h3>Need Further Assistance?</h3>
            <p>If you have any issues or need further assistance, please contact our support team:</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@budgetclaims.com">support@budgetclaims.com</a></p>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +1-800-123-4567</p>
            <p>Our support team is available Monday to Friday, from 9 AM to 5 PM PST.</p>
        </section>
